To sum buffer each cells: buffer of 4 i32, giving i32.
Let total be 0.
For each index i of cells: total becomes total plus cells at i.
Give total.

To main, giving i32.
Let cells be buffer of 4 i32 filled with 0.
cells at 0 becomes 1.
cells at 1 becomes 2.
cells at 2 becomes 3.
cells at 3 becomes 4.
Give sum buffer each cells.
